Going into my 2nd year with a 50HP etec. No problems so far. Nice quiet motor and very fuel efficient compared to by old 2 stroke.
been drooling over these for a couple years now  come on 649
It's no better or worse then any other engine on the market.

Into my 2nd yr with a 200HP on a 22' boat. Motor is awesome, less fuel consumption than an eqaul size fourstroke. Quiet, no smoke, sips oil.
